2
00:00:03,400 --> 00:00:06,400
♫ Love- love’s omelette rice ♫

3
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:08,600
♫ Don’t let it pass again  ♫

4
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:11,700
♫ If you’re sad, just cry, just cry ♫

5
